msgid "Death of Gwiti Ha’atel"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:137
msgid "My whole body still aches... Where the hell is this strange beach?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:142
msgid "The area was blighted. Not one human being was there."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:148
msgid "Apparently the dark gods have not yet completely abandoned me. The smell of the beast is in the air around here — perhaps they are the material for testing whether I shall survive. Conveniently for me, this ruin is piled high with corpses."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:165
msgid "With my mighty powers, monsters of this magnitude were not even an enemy!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:183
msgid "Noooo! Not now, not when I have escaped!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:197
msgid "Argh! I die!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:209
msgid "Who is hiding there?"
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: id=Corcyn, type=Dark Adept
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:230
msgid "Corcyn"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Corcyn
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:257
msgid "I almost got eaten by an ogre..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:262
msgid "You seem to be necromancer like me. Then come with me. Obey me and you will become more mighty."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:277
msgid "Death is good for the nagas that bother you!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:289
msgid "I am... defeated..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:297
msgid "The Wesnothians have discovered my escape! This is not good..."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=02_Brother_Against_Brother
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:7
msgid "Brother Against Brother"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Dark Acolyte, id=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:44
msgid "team_name^Nati"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Dark Acolyte, id=Nati Ha'atel
#. [unit]: id=Nati Ha'atel, type=Nightgaunt
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:65
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/11_An_Orcish_Coup.cfg:208
msgid "Nati Ha’atel"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:85
msgid "Defeat your brother Nati Ha’atel"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:98
msgid "As the sun set, Gwiti discovered that his arch-rival and brother, Nati, had already ensconced himself nearby."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:104
msgid "Ah, hated brother mine. Look well upon the setting sun, for you shall not live to see another in this land."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:109
msgid "This land? Do you truly not know where we are? Then you are a greater fool than I had thought."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:114
msgid "Cease your blustering, fool, and prepare to die... again."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:119
msgid "I will fight you with all my strength to prevent that, and I was always the stronger of us. Flee now and save your miserable hide before I make it a carpet."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:124
msgid "Don’t be silly! I’m not hairy enough to be a carpet! But your scalp would make a good pillow."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:139
msgid "What? I can’t die! I already have! Noooo!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:144
msgid "Ha ha ha, did I not tell you it would be so? Perhaps I shall summon your shade to serve me one day. Until then...farewell!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:149
msgid "It is over. I am doomed."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:163
msgid "I...have failed to win this battle. I am defeated. I will not believe it."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:168
msgid "Die, yes, die, and go to the Land of the Dead. Perhaps one day you will be back under my command!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:182
msgid "Didn’t I tell you so?!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:194
msgid "And by my own hands you died!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:206
msgid "I am Gwiti the Mighty, prepare to die!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:218
msgid "Now you shall die!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:226
msgid "You miserable wretch, know that it is only by my mercy that you look upon the sun again, for you shall die before it sets."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:231
msgid "May I remind you that even as we speak, my undead legions are marching towards you?"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=03_Skull_of_Morgorath
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:7
msgid "The Skull of Morgorath"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Karz Gholum
#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Isidal B'Tai
#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Nakur Kimoni
#. [side]: type=Orcish Warrior, id=Nagou
#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Vrork
#. [side]: type=Orcish Sovereign, id=Kogran
#. [side]: type=Orcish Sovereign, id=Eradush
#. [side]: type=Orcish Sovereign, id=Prirag
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:35
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:60
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:85
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:63
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/10_Return_to_the_Northlands.cfg:60
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/11_An_Orcish_Coup.cfg:62
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/11_An_Orcish_Coup.cfg:88
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/11_An_Orcish_Coup.cfg:114
msgid "team_name^Orcs"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Karz Gholum
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:52
msgid "Karz Gholum"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Isidal B'Tai
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:77
msgid "Isidal B’Tai"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Nakur Kimoni
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:102
msgid "Nakur Kimoni"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:128
msgid "Take the Skull of Morgorath"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:130
msgid "Destruction of Leganoth"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:142
msgid "After Gwiti destroyed his brother, he planned to march on Wesnoth to gain his revenge. But a Dark Spirit came to counsel him..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Leganoth
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:162
msgid "Gwitiii... Gwiti!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:167
msgid "A Dark Spirit? Surely this is a token of my mastery of the undead!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Leganoth
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:172
msgid "Gwiti, do not yet march in pursuit of your revenge. First, you shall go south, against the orcs, and there find the Skull of Morgorath."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:177
msgid "Speak on."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Leganoth
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:182
msgid "Do you see the three orc clans of this land? Their banners are topped with skulls, as is their custom. But one of these is the Skull of Morgorath — Take it and your power will grow greater by far."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Karz Gholum
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:190
msgid "Look! The undead are getting closer! My brethren, time for battle!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:202
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:180
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/10_Return_to_the_Northlands.cfg:225
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/12_Assault_on_Alduin.cfg:443
msgid "What? I can’t die! Noooo!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:216
msgid "You are not worthy of the Skull of Morgorath!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:236
msgid "That skull is powerless!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Leganoth
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:243
msgid "That is not the skull of Morgorath!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:250
msgid "Oh, no! The undead hordes have taken my banner!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:255
msgid "It is not your banner, and it never was! That skull has marked it as mine since long ago."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:267
msgid "Argh! This is only half of the skull, and near enough to powerless! Begone, Spirit!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:282
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/11_An_Orcish_Coup.cfg:470
msgid "Something is broken, please report."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/03_Skull_of_Morgorath.cfg:303
msgid "It’s been a long time since I fought anything myself!"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=04_Mages_And_Elves
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:7
msgid "Mages and Elves"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Great Mage, id=Quirind
#. [side]
#. [side]: type=Great Mage, id=Laellyn
#. [side]: type=Mage of Light, id=Menvan
#. [side]: type=Arch Mage, id=Caroran
#. [side]: type=Arch Mage, id=Aethacyn
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:36
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:35
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/12_Assault_on_Alduin.cfg:61
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/12_Assault_on_Alduin.cfg:100
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/12_Assault_on_Alduin.cfg:125
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/12_Assault_on_Alduin.cfg:150
msgid "team_name^Magi"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Great Mage, id=Quirind
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:63
msgid "Quirind"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Elvish Marshal, id=Lessalin
#. [side]: type=Elvish Hero, id=Urind
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:71
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:34
msgid "team_name^Elves"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Elvish Marshal, id=Lessalin
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:98
msgid "Lessalin"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:115
msgid "Move Gwiti to the Tower of Sorcery"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:116
msgid "Kill both enemy leaders"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:129
msgid "After sending the Dark Spirit away for his failure, Gwiti found some maps in the possession of the orc and realized that he was a short distance north of Wesnoth. Craving the power that was promised to him, he turned towards the Tower of Kaleon, where the greatest magi once studied."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:135
msgid "At last, I have reached the road. Unless I am far off my course, I should find the Tower of Kaleon here, filled with the secrets of ancient magi. Soon they shall all be mine, and my power will be great enough to invade Wesnoth."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Quirind
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:140
msgid "A dark sorcerer approaches! Can this be the same one that we banished?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Quirind
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:145
msgid "Accursed and dreadful one, know that we magi, guardians of the Tower of Kaleon, shall bar your way with all our spells! Flee now and you may survive."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lessalin
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:150
msgid "Quirind, know that you have the Elves at your back."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lessalin
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:155
msgid "Foul sorcerer of death, go far from this place or we shall send you to your own realm."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:160
msgid "Not born is the one that could challenge me!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:178
msgid "No! No! Noooo! It is over, I feel the shades reaching for me..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:192
msgid "Argh! I have fallen, and the Tower lies stripped of its defenses!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:209
msgid "Quirind, we have failed! You must guard the tower."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Quirind
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:219
msgid "Ah ha ha ha! The tower’s protective spells are now in force, you cannot enter without mastering a magic equal to it."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:233
msgid "Haha! I have gained entry to the tower!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lessalin
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:238
msgid "A curse upon that foul dark sorcerer!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/04_Mages_And_Elves.cfg:248
msgid "The way to the tower was opened!"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=05_Inside_The_Tower
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:5
msgid "Inside the Tower"
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: type=Elder Mage, id=Krimitros
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:58
msgid "Krimitros"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:84
msgid "Find Crelanu’s Book"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:97
msgid "If my memory serves, this tower should have three floors. I should be able to find the Book in a few hours...!"
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: type=Revenant, id=Xakan
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:106
msgid "Xakan"
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: type=Revenant, id=Karae
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:118
msgid "Karae"
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: type=Revenant, id=Pezit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:130
msgid "Pezit"
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: type=Revenant, id=Lagon
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:142
msgid "Lagon"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Karae
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:175
msgid "Hayaargghh! We have arrived! Command us, Master!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:197
msgid "Here’s he second floor! The mages can’t hide from us for long!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:210
msgid "The third floor! Closer! Find the Book!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:225
msgid "There’s a secret door here! This must be the library."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Krimitros
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:240
msgid "I will not allow the likes of you to lay eye upon the Book!"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=05_Inside_The_Tower
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:244
msgid "Well, well, well. Thirty-five pieces of gold were in this chest!"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=05_Inside_The_Tower
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:245
msgid "Blast it, the chest is empty!"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=05_Inside_The_Tower
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:246
msgid "Twenty pieces of gold is a welcome gift."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=05_Inside_The_Tower
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:247
msgid "I suppose thirty copper coins should not be scorned..."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=05_Inside_The_Tower
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:248
msgid "The chest is empty save for a few trinkets. The magic has gone out of them."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=05_Inside_The_Tower
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:249
msgid "Gack! This chest contains holy water!"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=05_Inside_The_Tower
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:250
msgid "Look at what the magi were guarding!"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=05_Inside_The_Tower
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:251
msgid "Those magi had hidden away more than it seemed!"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=05_Inside_The_Tower
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:252
msgid "Two dozen gold. Plundering this tower is fun!"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=05_Inside_The_Tower
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:253
msgid "A pile of assorted coins is here!"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=05_Inside_The_Tower
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:254
msgid "Haha, this chest holds scores of gold coins!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:269
msgid "Nooo! Not this close to the book!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:283
msgid "No! The Book must never fall into the hands of a necromancer!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:297
msgid "This is not the tome Crelanu wrote...hmmm... but it contains its whereabouts!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Xakan
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:302
msgid "We’re done in here! Let’s go slay some more enemies."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:330
msgid "Susanne"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/05_Inside_The_Tower.cfg:332
msgid "Congratulations! All your revenants survived."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=06_Crelanus_Book
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:5
msgid "Crelanu’s Book"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Elvish Hero, id=Urind
#. [unit]: id=Urind, type=Spectre
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:55
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:234
msgid "Urind"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Orcish Warrior, id=Nagou
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:84
msgid "Nagou"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:93
msgid "team_name^Enemies"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:117
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:267
msgid "Move Gwiti to take the book"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:118
msgid "Kill the elvish leader"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:131
msgid "Time marched on, and so did Gwiti. He was nearing the place where the dreadful tome of Crelanu was hidden."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:142
msgid "But the ancient magi had done their job well. The book had been hidden in a grove over which Elves and Orcs had waged war for many years, and any to approach would suffer their combined wrath..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Urind
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:148
msgid "Oh no. The orcs seem to have recruited the undead to their side."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nagou
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:153
msgid "Blast it! However did the elves get a dark sorcerer to march with them?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:158
msgid "I side not with either of you!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Nagou
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:163
msgid "A truce, then? I fear he will be the death of us both."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Urind
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:168
msgid "Very well. We have hated you Orcs for centuries, but the Undead are a danger to all that live."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:193
msgid "I die a terrible death... not knowing why."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:205
msgid "A curse upon that dark sorcerer! Why did he have to come here?!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:225
msgid "Rise from the depths of death!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Urind
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:258
msgid "Argh! My body is under control..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:263
msgid "You cannot escape me forever! Well, I must get the book."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:286
msgid "At last! This is it! Now I must laugh crazily as a true villain always does!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Advance Scout
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/06_Crelanus_Book.cfg:310
msgid "My lord, your suspicions were correct. There is indeed a dark sorcerer in this part of the country!"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=07_Confrontation
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:7
msgid "Confrontation"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=General, id=Leonard
#. [side]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:35
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:62
msgid "team_name^Wesnothians"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=General, id=Leonard
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:54
msgid "Leonard"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:102
msgid "Slay Leonard"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:115
msgid "With the finding of Crelanu’s ancient tome, fresh strength had flowed to Gwiti’s army, and they had made good time. However, Gwiti’s march was halted by Leonard as he reentered Wesnothian territory. The general of several outlying areas, his troops were many but untrained."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:121
msgid "I see that your puny kingdom marshals its troops at last."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Leonard
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:126
msgid "So you are the one responsible for our defeat at the Stone of Erzen. Die!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:131
msgid "Somehow, I have the feeling it is you who will do the dying today. I wonder why?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:136
msgid "In truth, Leonard’s army was unprepared and under-equipped, and he had neglected to send word. Luckily, behind him came one whose name was a bane to the undead: Lord Aretu. Gwiti knew that even if he defeated Leonard, his best hope was now to flee into the mountains."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Leonard
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:142
msgid "I shall slay you myself!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:154
msgid "So this is death... the cold, black void"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:168
msgid "No! This cannot be true! My king, I have failed..."
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: type=Paladin, id=Lord Aretu
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:180
msgid "Lord Aretu"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lord Aretu
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:195
msgid "Leonard is dead? Oh, what a sad day. Come, men, let us destroy those undead!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:200
msgid "Only one way lies open now. I must flee where his horses cannot go: the sharp peaks and bottomless caves."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:214
msgid "Move Gwiti to the end of the mountain pass"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Lord Aretu
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:235
msgid "Return to your master, dark fiend!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Leonard
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:266
msgid "Haha, it was a mistake of you to flee there! The pass is blocked, and my troops will slay you now!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:272
msgid "Phew... Surely the puny humans will be too tired to follow me now!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Tanar
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:291
msgid "Oh, no, escaping dwarves only to be caught by undead."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:296
msgid "Who are you? If you are a foe of the Dwarves, I might consider you an ally."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Tanar
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:301
msgid "I am Tanar, lord of an orcish clan that dwelt here! My people were driven out by the dwarves. All families count several dead. Please, let us march with you, for only a chance to strike back at the evil Dwarves!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:306
msgid "Gladly. I do get so lonely talking to myself, and none of my minions are worth talking to."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Tanar
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/07_Confrontation.cfg:311
msgid "Thank you, my new Lord! Never had I thought I would see the day when my people were glad to march alongside skeletons and ghosts."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=08_Underground_Pool
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:5
msgid "Underground Pool"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#. [event]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:24
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:146
msgid "Move Gwiti or Tanar into the water"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#. [event]
#. [case]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:32
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:148
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:142
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:188
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:221
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/10_Return_to_the_Northlands.cfg:160
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/11_An_Orcish_Coup.cfg:162
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/11_An_Orcish_Coup.cfg:423
msgid "Death of Tanar"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Dwarvish Berserker, id=Peluthlos
#. [side]: type=Dwarvish Lord, id=Geldar
#. [side]: type=Dwarvish Lord, id=Ainarthol
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:60
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:100
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:36
msgid "team_name^Dwarves"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Dwarvish Berserker, id=Peluthlos
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:77
msgid "Peluthlos"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Dwarvish Lord, id=Geldar
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:117
msgid "Geldar"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Tanar
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:160
msgid "We have come to a flooded part of the cave. If we forge ahead, the Dwarves should be delayed quite a bit."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Tanar
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:167
msgid "ARGH! What was that?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:172
msgid "I do not know. I guess, however, that some magic is at work in these caverns. Can you tell me anything of them?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Tanar
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:177
msgid "Nay, Lord. These passages were flooded higher last time I was here. The Dwarves did not delve here, and we shunned the nameless dread we felt."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:182
msgid "If there is anything to dread here, it is me. Now, onward!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:190
msgid "The Dwarves are still in these caves!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Tanar
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:195
msgid "Aye! They drove us out, and left a guard here to occupy us."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:200
msgid "Then we shall slay them. I have never had Dwarves rise to join my ranks. He, he, he, he..."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=08_Underground_Pool
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:221
msgid "The Hoard of the Dwarves! Three hundred pieces of gold at least!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:231
msgid "You swore you would protect me!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:245
msgid "I feel the darkness pulling me back..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:255
msgid "The paladins have caught up with us! We’re trapped!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/08_Underground_Pool.cfg:270
msgid "Death! You filthy orcs!"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=09_Underground_River
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:5
msgid "Underground River"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Dwarvish Lord, id=Ainarthol
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:57
msgid "Ainarthol"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Naga Myrmidon, id=Xoloss
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:80
msgid "team_name^Naga"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: type=Naga Myrmidon, id=Xoloss
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:108
msgid "Xoloss"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:140
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:186
msgid "Take over the dwarven castle"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:148
msgid "Your castle will sink at the start of turn 4."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Tanar
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:156
msgid "The water is rising behind us, it seems to be going back to its normal level."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:161
msgid "That should keep the dwarves and humans away. Let’s see what else these caves contain."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Tanar
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:177
msgid "Our castle has sunk!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:182
msgid "Maybe the midgets were running from the water... no matter, we can only move forward."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:210
msgid "The water will not flood past this chasm, get across and clear out the dwarves!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Tanar
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:215
msgid "Aye! Kill the dwarves!"
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:219
msgid "Wipe out enemies in the vicinity"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Tanar
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:262
msgid "We have cleared the area, Lord."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:267
msgid "Block the entrances. We will be safe here for a while. Now I have to study the book."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:272
msgid "End of Episode I"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:273
msgid "Gwiti’s adventure will continue in Episode II."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:384
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/10_Return_to_the_Northlands.cfg:239
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/11_An_Orcish_Coup.cfg:383
msgid "My clan will avenge this betrayal!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:398
msgid "Curse you dwarves! Curse you nagas! You will all die in this cave!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: The_Dark_Hordes/scenarios/09_Underground_River.cfg:406
msgid "With the power of the book, Gwiti collapsed the cave and brought down part of the mountain. Even some of the pursuing paladins were caught in the rubble."
msgstr ""

